{
  "stem": "935.4",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he had a lot of those, and he had a lot of these things here.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I didn't know what they meant.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he had, in his hand, these tiny pieces of paper, told me, screaming-- I don't know why they can't talk in a normal voice, but they don't; I think it's to scare you or something like that-- told me that they were found, and that I wasn't as clever as I thought.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I, because I didn't know how important he was, I just didn't care.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I told him that this is a lie.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It doesn't belong to me anyway, that I was a German actress trying to get to Germany, because in Holland, they didn't like Germans very much anymore.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And since it was impossible to get travel permission-- which was true; it took you forever, legitimate-- I went that way.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he said, is that why you crawl with Jews over the border?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I knew then that he wasn't sure that I'm a Jew or not.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm not.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I have nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm nothing.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said to me that-- he came back twice.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He handed it to me, these little pieces of paper, in an envelope and said that I had to give them to the commandant the next day.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I better, and he's going to spend the rest of his days to find out who I am.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if I lied to him, that I'm going to go straight to hell.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then he locked the cell, and then I was inside that stinking cell and saw nothing but names all over the place.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "With knife, with scissors, with fingernails-- all sorts of names.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I knew above me there was written in, or scribbled in, may tomorrow never come.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
